      "body" : "I'd rather drop the ability to skip reindex entirely, and require a timestamp for all imports. That way there is no possibility for confusion, and in the common case (it's a recently created key you're importing) it doesn't take particularly long anyway.\r\n\r\nI do agree we need to make reindexing abortable.",
